Can you avoid sepsis?
No

Make every effort to reduce your chances of becoming critically ill
#sepsis
#severesepsis
#septicshock

Common sense ways to help prevent #sepsis

Treat all infections early & properly

When possible, avoid situations infection may result from

Common sense~Prevent #sepsis
Wash hands often
Ensure those around U also wash often including Medical staff, beauticians, nail technicians

Common sense could save your life
Any and all infections can lead to #sepsis #severesepsis #septicshock. Don't let the clock start ticking

Someone dies as a result of #sepsis every
3rd
heartbeat
Do the math
Over 24,000 deaths every day
Be responsible for your own well being

IF you get manicure/pedicure
for GAWD's sake make sure your tech is washing her hands between each seat as she moves client 2 client
#sepsis
Better still ..don't put yourself in the high risk situation of getting nails done. Avoid all high risk activities when possible. #sepsis
